data.name: Dash FPS
data.detailed_description: Dash FPS isn't your average FPS. Our Players have the option to utilize Jetpacks, Super speed, and much more. We have added All-terrain vehicles and increased range on guns like the LMG. Now with many modes such as Capture the Flag, Solo, Team Deathmatch, ATV Conquest and more. With our new Full Multiplayer support you can join anyone online.
data.about_the_game: Dash FPS isn't your average FPS. Our Players have the option to utilize Jetpacks, Super speed, and much more. data.short_description: Dash FPS is a fun-filled Multiplayer First-Person Shooter with all kinds of new mechanics. Players have the option to utilize Jetpacks, Super speed, and much more. Play against our High Quality AI or battle against others on an online server.
